javadoc: ListingMergeConstants is an interface that provides constants that are used throughout all of the Listing merge managers for multi-user.
name: ListingMergeConstants
comment:
ListingMergeConstants is an interface that provides constants 
 that are used throughout all of the Listing merge managers for multi-user.
